---
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Strategic Marblism Partner</span>
      <h1>AI Employees clock in. <span class="grad">You cash out.</span></h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Hire your first AI team in days, not months. We help small businesses deploy Marblism's
        AI Employees — Penny, Eva, Sonny, Stan, Rachel, Linda — to handle the work that's
        eating your week.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Hire your AI team</a>
        <a href="#team" class="btn btn-ghost">Meet the team →</a>
      </div>
      <ul class="trust">
        <li>✓ Live in days</li>
        <li>✓ No code, no bloat</li>
        <li>✓ Pays for itself in week one</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="art" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
      <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
      <div class="card card-1">
        <div class="avatar a-1">E</div>
        <div class="meta">
          <strong>Eva</strong>
          <span>Drafted 12 replies</span>
        </div>
        <span class="status">●</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-2">
        <div class="avatar a-2">S</div>
        <div class="meta">
          <strong>Stan</strong>
          <span>Booked 3 demos</span>
        </div>
        <span class="status">●</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-3">
        <div class="avatar a-3">P</div>
        <div class="meta">
          <strong>Penny</strong>
          <span>Published 2 blogs</span>
        </div>
        <span class="status">●</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 96px 0 88px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(60% 60% at 80% 0%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.10), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(60% 60% at 0% 20%, rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.10), transparent 60%),
      var(--bg);
  }
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .grad {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-top: 18px;
  }
  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin: 28px 0 22px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .trust {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 18px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }
  .art {
    position: relative;
    height: 460px;
  }
  .orb {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(48px);
    opacity: 0.55;
  }
  .orb-1 { width: 280px; height: 280px; background: var(--accent); top: 20px; left: 30px; }
  .orb-2 { width: 240px; height: 240px; background: var(--accent-2); bottom: 30px; right: 10px; }
  .card {
    position: absolute;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    padding: 14px 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    width: 240px;
  }
  .card-1 { top: 30px; left: 0; }
  .card-2 { top: 170px; right: 0; }
  .card-3 { bottom: 20px; left: 60px; }
  .avatar {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .a-1 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #14b8a6, #06b6d4); }
  .a-2 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #ec4899); }
  .a-3 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #ec4899); }
  .meta { flex: 1; line-height: 1.3; }
  .meta strong { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--ink); display: block; }
  .meta span { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); }
  .status { color: #10b981; font-size: 0.7rem; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .art { height: 360px; }
  }
</style>
